duties_responsibilities.duty: Lead the strategy and day-to-day operations of channel partnerships.
Develop and generate new logo opportunities in collaboration with agents and channel integration manager.
Anticipate, troubleshoot, and collaborate among sales, account management, technical operations, and engineering teams to resolve issues.
Recruit, develop, and mentor agents, master agents & revenue generating partners in the assigned geographic area.
Establish and maintain a strategy to expand support for the company's vision of serving as the platform of record for channel partners.
Serve as the point of contact for channel partners in the assigned geographic area.

education_certification.credential: College degree or equivalent and 8 years field sales experience directly related to job (outside, partner sales experience) or 12 years job-related field sales experience; or an equivalent combination of education and job-related field sales experience required.
